---
title: Cheat's Italian Lamb & Veggie Bolognese with Penne, Pine Nuts & Parmesan
description: This bolognese packed with all the rich flavours of a classic Italian sauce will hardly have you believing it only took around half an hour to whip up. Silky silverbeet and carrot melt into this dish, creating a mouth-watering meal you'll remake time and time again.
